        // ----- CRVV1ETHSTETH-A 1st Stage Offboarding -----
        // Forum: https://forum.makerdao.com/t/stability-scope-parameter-changes-3/21238/6

        // Set CRVV1ETHSTETH-A Debt Ceiling to 0
