        // ----- Ecosystem Actor Dai Budget Stream -----

        // Chronicle Labs Auditor Wallet | 2023-07-01 00:00:00 to 2024-06-30 23:59:59 | 3,721,800 DAI | 0x68D0ca2d5Ac777F6A9b0d1be44332BB3d5981C2f
